               <p>They were a third time indicted for <rs id="t17711204-53-off279" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17711204-53-off279" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17711204-53-off279" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
